data.description: 60's style and charm walking distance to the heart of Fulton with views of Aransas Bay.  214 S Third street sits on an oversized corner lot, this 3 bed 2 bath home has a full efficiency apartment above the detached garage complete with full sized kitchen, full bath, closet space and stackable washer and dryer (conveys with sale).  Main house is 1578 square feet with a screened porch off of bedroom 3, large second living area could double as an additional bedroom, full laundry in house.  Guest quarters is 528 square feet with a screened porch that has amazing view of the bay.  Oversized 2 car garage with 2 overhead doors and additional w/d hookup.  All this and still plenty of yard space for enjoying the shade and breeze off the bay.  With a touch of elbow grease and a vision, this place could be an incredible water view home only steps from downtown Fulton.
